    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean \"overstated\" is a pretty strong word lol. but okay. what about the part about straining public services? if more people come in, even if they work, doesn't that naturally put more pressure on schools and hospitals? seems like a pretty factual consequence regardless of what the economists say about wages.",
